            "title": "盤中速報 - 恆生指數下跌-513.68點至24438.2點，跌幅2.06%",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>截至台北時間30日10:35，<a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/HSI\">恆生指數</a>下跌513.68點（或2.06%），暫報24438.20點。</p></section><p></p><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p><em>歷史漲跌幅</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul><li>近 1 週：-1.29%</li><li>近 1 月：-6.3%</li><li>近 3 月：-2.67%</li><li>近 6 月：-6.28%</li><li>今年以來：-2.65%</li></ul></section><section><p><em>焦點個股</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>禽畜肉類概念領跌-14.08%。其中    百利達集團控股(<a data-ga-click-item=\"HKS:08179:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/hkstock/quote/08179\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">08179-HK</a>)            下跌        66.67%            ;        中糧家佳康(<a data-ga-click-item=\"HKS:01610:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/hkstock/quote/01610\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">01610-HK</a>)            下跌        1.49%            ;        雨潤食品(<a data-ga-click-item=\"HKS:01068:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/hkstock/quote/01068\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">01068-HK</a>)            下跌        0.9%    。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>航空、航天及國防概念領跌-4.45%。其中    航天控股(<a data-ga-click-item=\"HKS:00031:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/hkstock/quote/00031\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">00031-HK</a>)            下跌        5.21%            ;        大陸航空科技控股(<a data-ga-click-item=\"HKS:00232:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"Ne